Package: slacR
Type: Package
Title: R-package to measure v and sigma from VIMOS IFU cubes
Version: 3.1.7
Date: 2014-12-13
Author: Oliver Czoske
Maintainer: Oliver Czoske <oliver.czoske@univie.ac.at>
Description: This package contains functions that read a IFS data cube
    (as prepared with VIPGI) and measures v and sigma through a direct
    pixel fitting method. Version 3 uses the modelling approach of
    Kelson et al. (2000) and incorporates also Gauss-Hermite modelling
    to order 4. 
License: GPL
